pital management inc bridgeway is a us quantitative investment management firm that employs several multifactor proprietary statistical models to assemble its investment portfolios as of  it had  billion of assets under management bridgeway specializes in domestic equities and is the adviser for bridgeway funds the company’s family of eleven noload mutual funds bridgeway also provides subadvisory and separate account services contents  history  investment procedures  bridgeway funds  references  external links historyedit in  john montgomery founded bridgeway in houston texas trained as an engineer montgomery began to develop his own models for portfolio management while pursuing his mba at harvard business school he began investing with the models in  and due to the success of these models he left his position in the transportation industry in  to undertake the founding of bridgeway the business plan that montgomery designed in  was unique in the asset management industry he established the benchmark that bridgeway would donate  of its net profits to nonprofit organizations included in montgomery’s business plan was a commitment to stewardship which bridgeway demonstrates by avoiding all soft dollar arrangements no fulltime employee is permitted to make seven times more than the lowest paid fulltime employee investment proceduresedit bridgeway employs a quantitative investment process the company believes that using a quantitative approach will eliminate biases and human emotions in the investment management process bridgeway applies up to  models with different factor weightings to diversify the risk associated with any one approach bridgeway tracks over  stocks and ranks each stock in the universe based on a number of factors bridgeway fundsedit the bridgeway funds family consists of  noload mutual funds and has no b fees publications such as barrons fortune kiplinger’s and money frequently rate bridgeway funds amongst their top picks referencesedit  bridgeway investment management team  bridgeway investment philosophy  bridgeway investment process  black box with a heart barrons july    the  best mutual funds kiplingers february   money  the best mutual funds you can buy money february  external linksedit company website bridgeway capital management retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlebridgewaycapitalmanagementoldid categories companies established in mutual fund familieshidden categories pages using deprecated image syntax navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontributionscreate accountlog in namespaces article talk variants views read edit view history more search navigation main pagecontentsfeatured contentcurrent eventsrandom articledonate to wikipediawikipedia store interaction helpabout wikipediacommunity portalrecent changescontact page tools what links hererelated changesupload filespecial pagespermanent linkpage informationwikidata itemcite this page printexport create a bookdownload as pdfprintable version languages add links this page was last edited on  june  at  text is available under the creative commons attributionsharealike license additional terms may apply by using this site you agree to the terms of use and privacy policy wikipedia® is a registered trademark of the wikimedia foundation inc a nonprofit organization privacy policy about wikipedia disclaimers contact wikipedia developers cookie statement mobile view bridgeway capital management  wikipedia bridgeway capital management from wikipedia the free encyclopedia   redirected from bridgeway capital management inc jump to navigation search bridgeway capital management type private industry financial services founded  founder john montgomery headquarters houston tx products investment management number of employees   website wwwbridgewaycom bridgeway capital management inc bridgeway is a us quantitative investment management firm that employs several multifactor proprietary statistical models to assemble its investment portfolio